Titolo: Ice Age (2002 video game)

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Ice Age is a 2002 platform game based on the film of the same name, developed by Artificial Mind and Movement, published by Ubi Soft and released exclusively for the Game Boy Advance. A sequel, Ice Age 2: The Meltdown, was released for all consoles in 2006, itself based on the film of the same name. A version for the PlayStation 2, Xbox, Microsoft Windows and GameCube was planned, but it is still cancelled.
It was also used as a runner-up prize during Cartoon Network's Frozen Fantasy Sweepstakes, where people would enter at CartoonNetwork.com, while the grand prize winner would get an Alaskan cruise for four, where they'll see glaciers.